relation: Darrow1 - #14 It's showtime! The Runaway Five begin their final act at the Chaos Theater. Also, Ness reveals that his backpack transforms into a nifty cape. Never leave home without it.
Darrow1 - #15 The Runaway Five, live in...comic.
Darrow1 - #16 Gorgeous shows off his skill in baking, while Lucky...well, got lucky he only lost his tie this time.
Darrow1 - #17 The song wraps up and the meeting with Poochyfud commences. Precious Moment figurines are very valuable in the criminal underworld, you know.
Darrow1 - #18 The Runaway Five gain their freedom and...show their distaste for proper entrances. Hey, when you look that cool, doors should just magically open for you anyways.
